title: Slide Hampton Interview by Monk Rowe - 7/30/2003 - W. Orange, NJ
uploader: Fillius Jazz Archive at Hamilton College
description:
Trombonist/arranger Slide Hampton shares stories about his musical upbringing, his prolific arranging career here and abroad, and the melodic role of the trombone.
